To compute the corresponding energies, 48-atom cells have been used for both perovskite structures, and the reported crystal structures for PbI264 and CrI265,66 have been used. In all cases the structures have been relaxed at the PBEsol level (see above). The energy balance of the mentioned reaction for x = 0.25 is then:2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
